'''尤絲拉·馬爾迪尼'''（{{bd|1998年|3月5日||}}），來自[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的[[游泳|游泳]][[运动员|运动员]]，现居于[[德国|德国]][[柏林|柏林]]。其为[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会难民代表团|2016奥运难民代表队]]（ROT）队员，2016年8月在[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]举行的[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會|2016年夏季奥运会]]参加游泳比赛。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/world/2016/03/18/olympic-dream-burns-bright-for-syrian-refugee.html|title=Swimmer Yusra Mardini hopes to compete at Rio Games for refugee squad in hopes of inspiring other Syrians.|last=Fahey|first=Ciaran|date=18 March 2016|newspaper=The Toronto Star|issn=0319-0781|access-date=19 March 2016|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820095724/https://www.thestar.com/news/world/2016/03/18/olympic-dream-burns-bright-for-syrian-refugee.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 传记 ==
馬爾迪尼生于一个叙利亚基督徒的家庭。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/07/29/meet-the-teen-who-escaped-war-in-syria-to-go-for-olympic-gold-6037566/|title=Meet the teen who escaped war in Syria to go for Olympic gold|date=29 Jul 2016|work=Metro.co.uk|accessdate=5 August 2016|author1=Ashitha Nagesh|archive-date=2016-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803161136/http://metro.co.uk/2016/07/29/meet-the-teen-who-escaped-war-in-syria-to-go-for-olympic-gold-6037566/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[大马士革|大马士革]]的居住期间，其受到[[敘利亞奧林匹克委員會|叙利亚奥委会]]的游泳培训。<ref name="guardian">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/mar/18/syria-rio-refugee-yusra-mardini-olympic-swimming|title=From Syria to Rio: refugee Yusra Mardini targets Olympic swimming spot|accessdate=25 March 2016|author=Philip Oltermann|work=the Guardian|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806185601/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/mar/18/syria-rio-refugee-yusra-mardini-olympic-swimming|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2012年，她代表叙利亚参加[[2012年世界短道游泳錦標賽|2012年世界短道游泳錦標賽]]中的200米混合式、200米自由式以及400米自由式的比赛。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.olympic.org/news/the-inspirational-olympic-journey-of-refugee-swimmer-yusra-mardini/248886|title=The inspirational Olympic journey of refugee swimmer Yusra Mardini|accessdate=25 March 2016|work=Olympic.org|publisher=[[奥运会|奥运会]]|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504104632/http://www.olympic.org/news/the-inspirational-olympic-journey-of-refugee-swimmer-yusra-mardini/248886|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]时，馬爾迪尼的房子被摧毁。<ref name="stuff">{{Cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/other-sports/78131048/Olympics-hopeful-Syrian-refugee-swims-for-three-hours-pushing-boat-of-migrants|title=Olympics hopeful Syrian refugee swims for three hours pushing boat of migrants|accessdate=25 March 2016|date=21 March 2016|work=Stuff|archive-date=2017-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820120301/http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/other-sports/78131048/Olympics-hopeful-Syrian-refugee-swims-for-three-hours-pushing-boat-of-migrants|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年8月。馬爾迪尼和她的姐姐萨拉决定逃离叙利亚。<ref name="npr">{{Cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/03/20/471180243/after-surviving-aegean-sea-syrian-swimmer-hopes-for-spot-in-olympics|title=After Surviving Aegean Sea, Syrian Swimmer Hopes For Spot In Olympics|accessdate=25 March 2016|date=20 March 2016|work=NPR.org|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809081328/http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2016/03/20/471180243/after-surviving-aegean-sea-syrian-swimmer-hopes-for-spot-in-olympics|dead-url=no}}</ref>她们先经过黎巴嫩，到达土耳其。从土耳其偷渡希腊的过程中，她们和18个其他难民被组织在一艘通常只能搭载6到7人的小船中；<ref name="guardian"/>在[[爱琴海|爱琴海]]中，这艘船的引擎停止工作，且船舱开始进水，于是馬爾迪尼和他的姐姐以及另外两名有游泳能力的人开始推动船只超过三小时，直到到达[[莱斯沃斯岛|莱斯沃斯]]。<ref name="npr"/>随后她们到达德国，并在2015年8月定居。<ref name="guardian"/>后其父母亦逃离叙利亚，到达德国。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://swimswam.com/refugee-swimmer-yusra-mardini-gets-chance-go-olympic-games/|title=Refugee swimmer Yusra Mardini gets a chance to go the Olympic Games|accessdate=25 March 2016|work=SwimSwam|archive-date=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924125031/https://swimswam.com/refugee-swimmer-yusra-mardini-gets-chance-go-olympic-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

馬爾迪尼继续在{{tsl|en|Wasserfreunde Spandau 04}}俱乐部接受游泳培训，并希望参加奥运会。<ref name="guardian"/><ref name="npr"/>她试图获得200米[[自由泳|自由泳]]的资格。<ref name="stuff"/>国际奥委会主席[[托马斯·巴赫|托马斯·巴赫]]谈及难民运动员，说：“我们帮助他们在没有战乱与暴力的环境下达成了展现杰出的运动技能的愿望。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.olympic.org/news/team-of-refugee-olympic-athletes-roa-created-by-the-ioc/248766|title=Team of Refugee Olympic Athletes (ROA) created by the IOC|accessdate=3 March 2016|publisher=IOC|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529020936/http://www.olympic.org/news/team-of-refugee-olympic-athletes-roa-created-by-the-ioc/248766|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年6月，她成为了参加奥运会的十名难民代表队运动员之一，参加2016夏奥会的100米自由泳和100米蝶泳项目。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://espn.go.com/olympics/story/_/id/15928002/syrian-swimmer-yusra-mardini-10-picked-ioc-form-refugee-team-rio-games |title=ESPN |accessdate=2016-08-06 |archive-date=2016-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710234723/http://espn.go.com/olympics/story/_/id/15928002/syrian-swimmer-yusra-mardini-10-picked-ioc-form-refugee-team-rio-games |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Wilder, Charly [http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/02/sports/olympics/a-swimmer-goes-from-syria-to-rio-from-refugee-to-olympian.html She Swam to Escape Syria.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/02/sports/olympics/a-swimmer-goes-from-syria-to-rio-from-refugee-to-olympian.html |date=20160807052529 }}</ref>

